c: 5
v: 33
t: "Kho omurungo kwa balia bakhupananga nende Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, nende okhukhola obubii khushialo, ni okhwirwa nohomba okhubambwa nohomba okhutetwa emikhono chiabu nende ebilenje buchikha, nohomba balondwe mushialo esho. Esho ni eshinyasio shiabu khushialo ne mwikulu balinyoola eshinyasio eshikhongo"